Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:03.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, all you viewers out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.95,0:00:07.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make \Nsure to keep the room nice and bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.12,0:00:09.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and sit back from the screen, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:15.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you to Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.17,0:00:16.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.71,0:00:18.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.34,0:00:19.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:21.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.50,0:02:01.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the ultimate vibe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.73,0:02:03.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.30,0:02:06.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia... Is this because \Nof the noise from that guitar?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.38,0:02:09.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:15.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Women who become my succubi \Ncan only hear my orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:21.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I captured both of you, \Nthe game would be booooring!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.05,0:02:25.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What I wanna see is a good \Ncat fight between two girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:29.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, one of those rip-roarin', \Njiggly, slippery, hair-pullin' affairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:30.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just the lowest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:32.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lowest?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:35.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the {\i1}highest{\i0} praise you could give me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:39.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for little babies who don't \Nunderstand rock to get spanked!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:44.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I just changed clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:47.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:52.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Which part should I devour first?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:55.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I should start with \Nthat dress! Too pretty for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.38,0:03:01.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heart's Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:06.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:13.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Get a \Nhold of yourself, Juvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.23,0:03:28.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia! You want to join Fairy Tail, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:31.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Attacking your allies isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:35.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you! Heyah! Feel the vibe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:37.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:40.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Water Cane!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.94,0:03:44.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, raise the roof with that red rhythm!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:46.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the soul of rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:47.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Says who?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.73,0:03:50.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want more cat-fight with claws!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.47,0:03:53.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it like she's trying to \Nsteal away a guy you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:55.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guy I like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:57.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Love Rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:59.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:03.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:06.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's completely under his control!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:08.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:12.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could beat Juvia \Nif she's fighting for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:17.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Die inside of Juvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.12,0:04:19.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:23.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy-san... Lucy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:25.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:28.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy-san... Juvia isn't doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:30.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Her heart is speaking to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.63,0:04:33.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia doesn't want to hurt her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:37.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps its presumptuous \Nfor me to say "friend..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:42.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that you are a rival in \Nmy love for Gray-sama, Lucy-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.28,0:04:43.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:48.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Juvia has come to love Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:53.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's welcoming, and fun, and a warm place...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:59.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even in the rain, it feels like \Nthe sun is out inside Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:05.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia had no idea it was okay to \Nsmile this much inside a guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:11.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I thought... And just when I felt \NI could finally become friends with everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:16.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia truly is a woman \Nthat brings misfortune...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:21.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tears... Even inside the water, \NJuvia's tears are warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:23.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia, baby! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:25.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time to finish her off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:34.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be the end for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.49,0:05:39.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,People who shed tears for their friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:42.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...will never be rejected from Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:46.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:49.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and boast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:52.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I remembered \Nsomething pretty neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:54.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:58.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and destroy her, Juvia baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:06:00.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:02.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tear you to shreds with my Water Jigsaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:06.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the big finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:08.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy-san, dodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:20.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Water Bearer, I open thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:22.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarius!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:25.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:28.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She called a Spirit using Juvia's body?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:32.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as there's water, I can summon \Nthe most powerful Spirit, Aquarius!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:34.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you, Juvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:38.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:40.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You bratty little girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:49.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you listen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.14,0:06:52.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that my hair can \Nabsorb water, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:56.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:06:58.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:07:00.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:02.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.47,0:07:11.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What... is this magical power?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:15.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those girls fused their magics together?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:17.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Unison Raid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:22.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this water?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:25.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is more than I can absorb!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.88,0:07:34.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sparking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:55.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.42,0:07:57.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia is back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:08:00.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad... I'm so glad, Juvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:03.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy-san, you're warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:08.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This might be the first time a \Nwoman has been nice to Juvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:14.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Don't go summoning \Nme in freaky places!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.94,0:08:18.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You better not be plannin' on summoning \Nme in a toilet bowl next, {\i1}right{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:20.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you, witch! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:22.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:23.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:25.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:28.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:33.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going on a vacation with \Nmy boyfriend for two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:36.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do {\i1}not{\i0} summon me, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:37.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:40.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a boyfriend yourself already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:41.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. As if that were possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:45.92,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,No boyfriend
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:43.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:45.92,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Unrequited
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:45.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy-san, love is very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:48.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:59.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We managed to get one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:02.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Things aren't going the way Jellal planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:06.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No... It was you who defeated him, Lucy-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:07.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:13.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You called me "Lucy" back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:17.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was glad you did. It made \Nus seem more like friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:20.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to add \N"-san" to my name anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:23.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're friends now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:30.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:34.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rain is falling from Juvia's eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:37.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a funny way of saying things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:42.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wait a little while \Nwe recover our strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.25,0:09:46.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Juvia will as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.28,0:09:53.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Unison Raid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:58.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that monk spent his entire \Nlife studying in pursuit of?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:10:02.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard in the end he never attained it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:06.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's coincidence, that's \Nquite the nerve they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:11.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They may be little girls, but \Nthey are Erza's comrades, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:35.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On the subject of attacking the \NTower of Heaven with Etherion:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:38.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,4 people for, 5 people against.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:43.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As it stands we will resolve \Nto hold off using Etherion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:44.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:47.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you people really comprehend \Nthe situation we are in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:49.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make a scene, Sieg...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.47,0:10:51.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've already had your say! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.39,0:10:54.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are still peaceful \Nways of solving this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:56.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Peaceful?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:11:00.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,While we're wasting time \Ndoing this pointless farce,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.21,0:11:03.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal is resurrecting the dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:05.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you feel it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:08.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The overflowing negative magical power...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.15,0:11:11.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the horror of who \Nhe is trying to resurrect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:12.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.53,0:11:15.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Siegrain, what exactly are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:20.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I held back this information on the slight \Nchance that it would leak out and cause panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:25.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:26.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:28.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Wizard Zeref!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:34.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:36.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sieg!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.87,0:11:38.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:41.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand Jellal better than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:44.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he's my twin brother, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:48.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We will vote once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:55.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoo-hoot Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:59.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Talons of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:07.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You thought that would work?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:11.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a match for Natsu! That owl's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:12.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:14.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's one of Trinity Raven.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:19.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to to drop the iron \Nhammer of justice upon you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:25.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Missile Hoo-hoo-hoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:29.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And? Think that'd hit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:31.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:35.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Arm hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.91,0:12:43.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Around the World!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:46.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His techniques are nonsensical, but fearsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:51.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:54.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know your weakness, Salamander!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:57.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! That's transportation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:12:57.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:13:00.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu can't handle transportation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:03.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Going in for the kill when \Nyour opponent is weakened!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:05.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That{\i0} is hunting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:12.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Capture Hoo-hoo-hoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:18.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:22.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:26.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:30.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I supposed to be super lucky today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:32.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The result will be the same every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.59,0:13:35.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And wait, why wouldn't \Nyou be happy with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:37.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Super lucky my butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:40.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This morning I got stuck in \Na ditch, lost my wallet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:42.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothin' good has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:53.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:55.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes another weirdo, sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:13:59.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the place Grandpa Rob talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:07.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.67,0:14:08.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.81,0:14:10.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:16.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's being eaten whole?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:20.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I digest the magical power \Nof people I feed on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:22.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give back Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:26.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Hoo-hoo-hoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.39,0:14:27.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.08,0:14:28.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:35.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's digesting Salamander's magical \Npower and taking it for himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.61,0:14:36.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:40.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the skill of the Assassin's Guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:42.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The final blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:50.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh... That's some crazy-hot fire there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.69,0:14:51.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:54.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A new challenger appears!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:14:57.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, weren't you supposed \Nto go after Sho and Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.82,0:14:59.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's held us up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:02.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to find them quick \Nor we're in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:07.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal said that he was planning \Non using Erza as a human sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.68,0:15:12.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think there's anyone who \Ncan beat Erza when she's serious,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:16.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but she's too defenseless while \Nshe's trapped inside that card!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:20.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a mistake to tell \NSho everything all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:23.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I never thought he'd go crazy like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:25.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:28.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Save Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:33.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I always gotta save your butt... 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:36.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we supposed to do if \Nyou get yourself eaten, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:38.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You flaming piece of...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.28,0:15:42.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Digestion has begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:46.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In about 10 minutes Salamander's \Nbody with be dissolved!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:51.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And when that happens, his \Nmagical powers will be all mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:57.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:16:00.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so cocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:04.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:12.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:16.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dodge it! He has the same \Nmagic as Salamander!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:22.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't use ice within fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:26.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:27.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:33.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are Salamander's friend, than you \Nshould know how powerful these flames are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:46.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always by herself, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:49.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go talk to her, Cana?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.33,0:16:52.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She totally ignored me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:57.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't like it when a newcomer \Ndoesn't introduce herself to me, the great Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:17:00.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when did you start \Nbeing such hot stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.82,0:17:04.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:12.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:15.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a wizard's guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:17.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't a place to be wearing armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:19.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about you wear \Nsomething yourself, knave?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.95,0:17:21.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a guild for perverts?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.51,0:17:24.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She sure told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:26.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Got to give her that one, Gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.89,0:17:29.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:30.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not concern yourself with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:39.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The flames are freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:42.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You call these Natsu's flames?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:43.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:46.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're nothing but a damn poser!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:49.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some impressive \Nmagical power you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.43,0:17:52.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll capture you as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:54.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:57.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:18:01.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ack, that's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:05.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time to be wasting here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:07.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to catch up to Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:11.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get beat up by Erza again, Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.85,0:18:14.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't give up, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:15.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be you're in love?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.91,0:18:16.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:20.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's pretty amazing being \Nable to get Gray like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:24.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the future of Fairy Tail will \Nride on the back of Erza the Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:28.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to accept her as one of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:31.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to bring Erza back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:40.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've found you, Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:43.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, it's on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:45.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I'm finally going to beat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:52.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:56.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, you never learn, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:18:59.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Have at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:03.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:06.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You surrender already?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:12.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you always by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:18.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I like being by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:21.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel uncomfortable around other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:22.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:26.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you crying all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:42.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't have at me today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:44.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:54.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:55.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:19:58.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.59,0:20:03.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:06.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven Slice Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:18.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.93,0:20:21.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She was always...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.83,0:20:24.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...by herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:26.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...her heart clad in armor...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.30,0:20:29.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...crying, all alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:35.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:37.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:41.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza must be in Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:44.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So she no longer sheds those tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:48.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,8 people in agreement, 1 against.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.57,0:20:55.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, Etherion is given permission \Nto fire upon the Tower of Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.10,0:21:00.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a decision from the Council!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:21:01.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Etherion will fire in one hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:21:01.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Start the preparations! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:13.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:16.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.60,0:21:18.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elder Yajima...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.95,0:21:22.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sieg... Are you really sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.98,0:21:26.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think about it carefully once again,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.20,0:21:29.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,there might yet be another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:32.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You may not agree with our methods,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.16,0:21:36.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but we cannot allow Zeref to be resurrected.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.79,0:21:40.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know this, right, Elder Yajima?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.91,0:21:46.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.30,0:21:49.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You will take full \Nresponsibility! Right, Sieg?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.42,0:21:51.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. All responsibility lies with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.45,0:21:54.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What I meant is that you will be \Nresponsible for the lives you will take!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.88,0:22:00.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are trying to send your \Nown twin brother to oblivion!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.36,0:22:05.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You will have to carry that loss of life on \Nyour back for the rest of your life, Sieg!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.10,0:22:10.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will bear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.26,0:22:12.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will bear the weight of Jellal's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.52,0:22:18.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what will you do? There's no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.77,0:22:22.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon the light will rain down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.53,0:23:59.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what happened to the bird brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.21,0:24:02.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray beat him while you were unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.53,0:24:05.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Damn that underpants man!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.65,0:24:08.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare he steal all the good parts!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.06,0:24:10.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight again!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.10,0:24:13.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, we don't have time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.10,0:24:16.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.55,0:24:20.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway, beating Jellal \Nwould be way more impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.12,0:24:21.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.93,0:24:23.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.45,0:24:25.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worn out...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.35,0:24:27.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
